{"tid":1486220,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［日本社運失敗的歷史］","createTime":"2019-08-18T20:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T23:28:50.000Z","uid":25825,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"530fbdde458219443b2f3ee88fa955c497a593e2","tid":1486220,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:43:30.000Z","msg":"［日本社運失敗的歷史］<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@whyvan123/日本社運失敗的歷史-3c27812b1042\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40whyvan123%2F%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%A4%BE%E9%81%8B%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2-3c27812b1042&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSskoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=11765093\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@whyvan123/日本社運失敗的歷史-3c27812b1042</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作者提醒抗爭者，當年日本社運的致命傷，就是過度強調「苦行」，社運人士無論是自己或同路人的要求太高，也不讓人抗爭容下一點輕鬆，不容忍抗爭者可以有一絲快樂．如此思考方法，讓日本社運走入互相批鬥，失去了主流社會支持的死胡同．<br />\n<br />\n「自我反省由於帶着強烈倫理色彩，忠於這些原則的運動者，會去攻擊不如自己認真看待運動的戰友，或是在沒辦法堅持原則的時候感到挫折．運動者無法對戰友採取寬容的態度，導致內部衝突和暴力，太着重於抽象的理念，容易陷入自以為是的危險」"},{"pid":"b00bacbeb2cdc075de6b51f45c89aa90f46756f4","tid":1486220,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:43:39.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"d049ff93f3be926b8e359ac8ae40b95240b548bd","tid":1486220,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:43:50.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"cf43162212fd2df80d74d07dcc6603491d409bbf","tid":1486220,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:44:01.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"4e9a4141b561f8c0b86fb52aff3fce7747d43e14","tid":1486220,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:44:11.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"89325e3b7aff692d0ba97d753e65c8d0be18a669","tid":1486220,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:44:22.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"ac4c8d99696db9214262cbf769e41746594bd66a","tid":1486220,"uid":295304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cited